00:17:26,215 --> 00:17:27,375
Prosím?

175
00:17:27,416 --> 00:17:28,883
Přines ji znovu

176
00:17:29,919 --> 00:17:30,943
Ano, madam

177
00:17:39,562 --> 00:17:42,395
Přines mi ji opět zítra ráno

178
00:17:43,499 --> 00:17:44,932
Prosím?

179
00:17:48,037 --> 00:17:49,629
Ano, madam

